    <thetext>Description of problem:
+ and - buttons in QSpinBox in adwaita style w/ Qt5.6.0 eat up all the space reserved for the widget, as can be seen in the screenshot http://wiki.lyx.org/uploads/Playground/LyX-Fedora24-Qt560.png
LEFT (green): LyX 2.1.4 w/ Qt 4.8.7 that comes with Fedora 24, running in VBox
RIGHT (yellow): LyX 2.2dev w/ Qt 5.6.0 compiled on Fedora 24, running in VBox
BOTTOM LEFT (red): LyX 2.2dev w/ 5.6.0 running on Fedora 23, natively, HiDPI screen, 3200x1800


Steps to Reproduce:
1. Build LyX with Qt5.6.0 on Fedora 24
2. QSpinBox won&apos;t render completely in dialogs



Additional info:</thetext>
